joint venture agreement, the Liberia-Nigeria Chamber of Commerce
said today.
</P>
<P>
A feasibility study is also being carried out to facilitate
the establishment of a sugar factory and a tea-blending industry
in that country, according to the chamber's president Chief
Anthony Anyaso.
</P>
<P>
