<HEADLINE> Leading Chemical Works Begins Operation in Northwest China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XI'AN, December 28 (Xinhua) -- The largest chemical works in
northwest China has begun operations in a high-tech development
zone in Weinan City, Shaanxi Province.
</P>
