government to overseas business people, Yangpu Economic
Development Zone covers an area of 27.35 square kilometers.
</P>
<P>
Han Zhizhong, vice-governor of Hainan, said today that the
operation of the first industrial project in the zone confirmed
the province's confidence to develop the Yangpu area. 
