Chaharmahal Bakhtiari, but no one was killed.
</P>
<P>
According to Iran's official news agency IRNA, the helicopter
belonging to the Iranian army crashed in the village of Shoush, 30
kilometers from Lordegan. It was on a mission to cooperate with
Mahab Qods company which is implementing a dam project in the
area.
</P>
<P>
