forces said that the helicopter was flying at a low altitude due
to some technical difficulties, adding that only the flight crew
and two technicians of the Mahab Qods company were injured.
</P>
<P>
The injured received out-patient treatment in Lordegan
Emergency Center and one of them was sent to Boroujen, another
city of the province, for hospitalization.
</P>
<P>
However, there is no report about the extent of damage of the
helicopter or how many people on board. 
</P>
