Vision, a Christian organization which offers assistance to
different groups of people, his organization has spent 6.7
million Zimbabwe Dollars (480,000 U.S. Dollars) in providing
water reservoirs, seed packs of drought tolerant crops, 110 tons
of sorghum and millet as well as various food stocks to be used
during the drought period.
</P>
<P>
