other business facilities in town were also damaged.
</P>
<P>
Police moved in and restored order by 3 a.m. Saturday. It's
reported that the situation there remained very tense until
nightfall, though additional police and army personnel have been
deployed to prevent further clash.
</P>
<P>
Police are hopeful that normalcy would return by Sunday.
