<HEADLINE> Anand, Adams Draw Second Chess Match </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GRONINGEN, Netherlands, December 27 (Xinhua) -- Viswanathan
Anand of India and Michael Adams of England drew their second
match in the best-of-four World Chess Championship eliminator in
Groningen of the Netherlands on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
